# This content is from "Contribution-Guide.md", line 1
msgctxt "chunk_53390D48"
msgid "# Contributing to the Project\n"
msgstr "# 为项目做贡献\n"

# This content is from "Contribution-Guide.md", line 3
msgctxt "chunk_A71D833E"
msgid "> [!CAUTION]\n>\n> The current project maintainers are researching automated documentation internationalization. Therefore, any PRs related to documentation internationalization/translation will NOT be accepted!\n>\n> Please do NOT submit PRs related to documentation internationalization/translation!\n"
msgstr "> [!CAUTION]\n>\n> 当前项目维护者正在研究自动化文档国际化方案。因此，任何与文档国际化/翻译相关的PR将不被接受！\n>\n> 请勿提交与文档国际化/翻译相关的PR！\n"

# This content is from "Contribution-Guide.md", line 9
msgctxt "chunk_D57757D9"
msgid "Thank you for your interest in this project! Before you start contributing, please take some time to read the following guidelines to ensure your contribution can be smoothly accepted.\n"
msgstr "感谢您对本项目的关注！在开始贡献之前，请花些时间阅读以下指南，以确保您的贡献能够顺利被采纳。\n"

# This content is from "Contribution-Guide.md", line 11
msgctxt "chunk_FB836CBD"
msgid "## Types of Contributions Not Accepted\n"
msgstr "## 不接受的贡献类型\n"

# This content is from "Contribution-Guide.md", line 13
msgctxt "chunk_F2331818"
msgid "1. Documentation internationalization/translation\n2. Contributions related to core infrastructure, such as HTTP API, etc.\n3. Issues explicitly marked as \"No help needed\" (including issues in the [Byaidu/PDFMathTranslate](Byaidu/PDFMathTranslate) and the [PDFMathTranslate/PDFMathTranslate-next](PDFMathTranslate/PDFMathTranslate-next) repository).\n4. Other contributions deemed inappropriate by the maintainers.\n5. Contributing documentation, but changing the documentation in languages other than English.\n6. PRs that require modifying PDF files.\n"
msgstr "1. 文档国际化/翻译  \n2. 与核心基础设施相关的贡献，例如 HTTP API 等  \n3. 明确标记为“无需帮助”的问题（包括 [Byaidu/PDFMathTranslate](Byaidu/PDFMathTranslate) 和 [PDFMathTranslate/PDFMathTranslate-next](PDFMathTranslate/PDFMathTranslate-next) 仓库中的问题）  \n4. 维护者认为不合适的其他贡献  \n5. 贡献文档，但修改非英语语言的文档  \n6. 需要修改 PDF 文件的 PR\n"

# This content is from "Contribution-Guide.md", line 20
msgctxt "chunk_7828B7C7"
msgid "Please do NOT submit PRs related to the above types.\n"
msgstr "请勿提交与上述类型相关的PR。\n"

# This content is from "Contribution-Guide.md", line 22
msgctxt "chunk_56FADEC9"
msgid "> [!NOTE]\n>\n> If you want to contribute documentation, please **only modify the English version of the documentation**. Other language versions are translated by contributors themselves.\n"
msgstr "> [!NOTE]\n>\n> 如果你想贡献文档，请**仅修改文档的英文版本**。其他语言版本由贡献者自行翻译。\n"

# This content is from "Contribution-Guide.md", line 26
msgctxt "chunk_485712CB"
msgid "## Contribution Process\n"
msgstr "## 贡献流程\n"

# This content is from "Contribution-Guide.md", line 28
msgctxt "chunk_4D698FBF"
msgid "1. Fork this repository and clone it locally.\n2. Create a new branch: `git checkout -b feature/<feature-name>`.\n3. Develop and ensure your code meets the requirements.\n4. Commit your code:\n   ```bash\n   git add .\n   git commit -m \"<semantic commit message>\"\n   ```\n5. Push to your repository: `git push origin feature/<feature-name>`.\n6. Create a PR on GitHub, provide a detailed description, and request a review from [@awwaawwa](https://github.com/awwaawwa).\n7. Ensure all automated checks pass.\n"
msgstr "1. Fork 此仓库并在本地克隆它。\n2. 创建新分支：`git checkout -b feature/<feature-name>`。\n3. 开发并确保代码符合要求。\n4. 提交代码：\n   ```bash\n   git add .\n   git commit -m \"<semantic commit message>\"\n   ```\n5. 推送至你的仓库：`git push origin feature/<feature-name>`。\n6. 在 GitHub 上创建 PR，提供详细描述，并请求 [@awwaawwa](https://github.com/awwaawwa) 进行审核。\n7. 确保所有自动化检查通过。\n"

# This content is from "Contribution-Guide.md", line 40
msgctxt "chunk_89A6F55A"
msgid "> [!TIP]\n>\n> You do not need to wait until your development is fully complete to create a PR. Creating one early allows us to review your implementation and provide suggestions.\n>\n> If you have any questions about the source code or related matters, please contact the maintainer at aw@funstory.ai.\n>\n> Resource files for version 2.0 are shared with [BabelDOC](https://github.com/funstory-ai/BabelDOC). The code for downloading related resources is in BabelDOC. If you want to add new resource files, please contact the BabelDOC maintainer at aw@funstory.ai.\n"
msgstr "> [!TIP]\n>\n> 你无需等到开发完全完成才创建PR。提前创建PR可以让我们审查你的实现并提供建议。\n>\n> 如果对源代码或相关事宜有任何疑问，请联系维护者 aw@funstory.ai。\n>\n> 2.0版本的资源文件与[BabelDOC](https://github.com/funstory-ai/BabelDOC)共享。下载相关资源的代码位于BabelDOC中。如需添加新的资源文件，请联系BabelDOC维护者 aw@funstory.ai。\n"

# This content is from "Contribution-Guide.md", line 48
msgctxt "chunk_E7638696"
msgid "## Basic Requirements\n"
msgstr "## 基本要求\n"

# This content is from "Contribution-Guide.md", line 50
msgctxt "chunk_4D251FB3"
msgid "<h4 id=\"sop\">1. Workflow</h4>\n"
msgstr "<h4 id=\"sop\">1. 工作流程</h4>\n"

# This content is from "Contribution-Guide.md", line 52
msgctxt "chunk_8FDDA473"
msgid "   - Please fork from the `main` branch and develop on your forked branch.\n   - When submitting a Pull Request (PR), provide a detailed description of your changes.\n   - If your PR does not pass automated checks (indicated by `checks failed` and a red cross), please review the corresponding `details` and modify your submission to ensure the new PR passes all checks.\n\n"
msgstr "   - 请从 `main` 分支进行 fork，并在你 fork 的分支上进行开发。\n   - 提交 Pull Request (PR) 时，请提供详细的变更说明。\n   - 如果你的 PR 未通过自动化检查（显示为 `checks failed` 并带有红色叉号），请查看对应的 `details` 并修改提交内容，确保新 PR 能通过所有检查。\n\n"

# This content is from "Contribution-Guide.md", line 57
msgctxt "chunk_19D447DF"
msgid "<h4 id=\"dev&test\">2. Development and Testing</h4>\n"
msgstr "<h4 id=\"dev&test\">2. 开发与测试</h4>\n"

# This content is from "Contribution-Guide.md", line 59
msgctxt "chunk_65AB8932"
msgid "   - Use the command `pip install -e .` for development and testing.\n\n"
msgstr "   - 使用命令 `pip install -e .` 进行开发和测试。\n\n"

# This content is from "Contribution-Guide.md", line 62
msgctxt "chunk_B4865580"
msgid "<h4 id=\"format\">3. Code Formatting</h4>\n"
msgstr "<h4 id=\"format\">3. 代码格式化</h4>\n"

# This content is from "Contribution-Guide.md", line 64
msgctxt "chunk_E8324FFA"
msgid "   - Configure the `pre-commit` tool and enable `black` and `flake8` for code formatting.\n\n"
msgstr "   - 配置 `pre-commit` 工具并启用 `black` 和 `flake8` 进行代码格式化。\n\n"

# This content is from "Contribution-Guide.md", line 67
msgctxt "chunk_7A584B10"
msgid "<h4 id=\"requpdate\">4. Dependency Updates</h4>\n"
msgstr "<h4 id=\"requpdate\">4. 依赖项更新</h4>\n"

# This content is from "Contribution-Guide.md", line 69
msgctxt "chunk_BE2E8298"
msgid "   - If you introduce new dependencies, please update the dependency list in the `pyproject.toml` file in a timely manner.\n\n"
msgstr "   - 如果引入了新的依赖项，请及时更新 `pyproject.toml` 文件中的依赖列表。\n\n"

# This content is from "Contribution-Guide.md", line 72
msgctxt "chunk_1615D8D8"
msgid "<h4 id=\"docupdate\">5. Documentation Updates</h4>\n"
msgstr "<h4 id=\"docupdate\">5. 文档更新</h4>\n"

# This content is from "Contribution-Guide.md", line 74
msgctxt "chunk_725E4B8A"
msgid "   - If you add new command-line options, please update the list of command-line options in all language versions of the `README.md` file accordingly.\n\n"
msgstr "   - 如果添加了新的命令行选项，请在所有语言版本的 `README.md` 文件中相应更新命令行选项列表。\n\n"

# This content is from "Contribution-Guide.md", line 77
msgctxt "chunk_09178615"
msgid "<h4 id=\"commitmsg\">6. Commit Messages</h4>\n"
msgstr "<h4 id=\"commitmsg\">6. 提交信息</h4>\n"

# This content is from "Contribution-Guide.md", line 79
msgctxt "chunk_8007BC97"
msgid "   - Use [Conventional Commits](https://www.conventionalcommits.org/en/v1.0.0/), for example: `feat(translator): add openai`.\n\n"
msgstr "   - 使用 [约定式提交](https://www.conventionalcommits.org/en/v1.0.0/)，例如：`feat(translator): add openai`。\n\n"

# This content is from "Contribution-Guide.md", line 82
msgctxt "chunk_F5439516"
msgid "<h4 id=\"codestyle\">7. Coding Style</h4>\n"
msgstr "<h4 id=\"codestyle\">7. 代码风格</h4>\n"

# This content is from "Contribution-Guide.md", line 84
msgctxt "chunk_22ECCE1D"
msgid "   - Ensure your submitted code adheres to basic coding style standards.\n   - Use either snake_case or camelCase for variable naming.\n\n"
msgstr "   - 确保提交的代码符合基本的编码风格标准。\n   - 变量命名请使用 snake_case 或 camelCase。\n\n"

# This content is from "Contribution-Guide.md", line 88
msgctxt "chunk_2F60B8EB"
msgid "<h4 id=\"doctypo\">8. Documentation Formatting</h4>\n"
msgstr "<h4 id=\"doctypo\">8. 文档格式</h4>\n"

# This content is from "Contribution-Guide.md", line 90
msgctxt "chunk_320F91BE"
msgid "   - For `README.md` formatting, please follow the [Chinese Copywriting Guidelines](https://github.com/sparanoid/chinese-copywriting-guidelines).\n   - Ensure that both English and Chinese documentation are always up to date; other language documentation updates are optional.\n"
msgstr "   - 对于 `README.md` 的格式，请遵循[中文文案排版指北](https://github.com/sparanoid/chinese-copywriting-guidelines)。\n   - 确保英文和中文文档始终保持最新；其他语言文档的更新为可选。\n"

# This content is from "Contribution-Guide.md", line 93
msgctxt "chunk_126AF33C"
msgid "## Adding a Translation Engine\n"
msgstr "## 添加翻译引擎\n"

# This content is from "Contribution-Guide.md", line 95
msgctxt "chunk_38A36DFF"
msgid "1. Add a new translator configuration class in the `pdf2zh/config/translate_engine_model.py` file.\n2. Add an instance of the new translator configuration class to the `TRANSLATION_ENGINE_SETTING_TYPE` type alias in the same file.\n3. Add the new translator implementation class in the `pdf2zh/translator/translator_impl` folder.\n"
msgstr "1. 在 `pdf2zh/config/translate_engine_model.py` 文件中添加一个新的翻译器配置类。\n2. 在同一文件中将新的翻译器配置类实例添加到 `TRANSLATION_ENGINE_SETTING_TYPE` 类型别名中。\n3. 在 `pdf2zh/translator/translator_impl` 文件夹中添加新的翻译器实现类。\n"

# This content is from "Contribution-Guide.md", line 99
msgctxt "chunk_5B4684E1"
msgid "> [!NOTE]\n>\n> This project does not intend to support any translation engines with an RPS (requests per second) lower than 4. Please do not submit support for such engines.\n"
msgstr "> [!NOTE]\n>\n> 本项目无意支持任何 RPS（每秒请求数）低于 4 的翻译引擎。请勿提交对此类引擎的支持。\n"

# This content is from "Contribution-Guide.md", line 103
msgctxt "chunk_7ED6230D"
msgid "## Project Structure\n"
msgstr "## 项目结构\n"

# This content is from "Contribution-Guide.md", line 105
msgctxt "chunk_9004E6A3"
msgid "- **config folder**: Configuration system.\n- **translator folder**: Translator-related implementations.\n- **gui.py**: Provides the GUI interface.\n- **const.py**: Some constants.\n- **main.py**: Provides the command-line tool.\n- **high_level.py**: High-level interfaces based on BabelDOC.\n- **http_api.py**: Provides HTTP API (not started).\n"
msgstr "- **config 文件夹**：配置系统。\n- **translator 文件夹**：翻译器相关实现。\n- **gui.py**：提供 GUI 界面。\n- **const.py**：一些常量。\n- **main.py**：提供命令行工具。\n- **high_level.py**：基于 BabelDOC 的高级接口。\n- **http_api.py**：提供 HTTP API（未启动）。\n"

